%N A313571 Coordination sequence Gal.5.169.3 where Gal.u.t.v denotes the coordination sequence for a vertex of type v in tiling number t in the Galebach list of u-uniform tilings.
%C A313571 Note that there may be other vertices in the Galebach list of u-uniform tilings with u <= 6 that have this same coordination sequence. See the Galebach link for the complete list of A-numbers for all these tilings.
%H A313571 Brian Galebach, <a href="/A250120/a250120.html">k-uniform tilings (k <= 6) and their A-numbers</a>
%F A313571 Conjectures from _Chai Wah Wu_, May 16 2026: (Start)
%F A313571 a(n) = 2*a(n-7) - a(n-14) for n > 17.
%F A313571 G.f.: (-x^17 - x^15 + 2*x^14 + 4*x^13 + 12*x^12 + 14*x^11 + 20*x^10 + 26*x^9 + 29*x^8 + 33*x^7 + 29*x^6 + 24*x^5 + 19*x^4 + 14*x^3 + 10*x^2 + 5*x + 1)/(x^14 - 2*x^7 + 1). (End)
